[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0deb/1c54/413_large.png?m=1610122546", "name": "programming", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0deb/1c54/413_normal.png?m=1610122546", "title": "编程", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programming", "topics": 1420, "footer": "", "header": "Have fun and make money and art.", "title_alternative": "Programming", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0deb/1c54/413_mini.png?m=1610122546", "stars": 2296, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 413, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 75489, "username": "stevenrao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/stevenrao", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50a3/beeb/75489_mini.png?m=1414069147", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50a3/beeb/75489_normal.png?m=1414069147", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50a3/beeb/75489_large.png?m=1414069147", "created": 1411967901, "last_modified": 1414069147, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "WillingXyz", "last_touched": 1775366036, "title": "AI 写代码真香喷；以后只要产品经理就可以了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203613", "created": 1775356210, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 🚀 只用了 2 天，一行代码没写\r\n\r\n说出来你可能不信，这个项目我一行代码都没写。\r\n\r\n我的工作流程是这样的：\r\n1. 📝 和 AI 聊需求，确定要做什么功能\r\n2. 📄 写成详细的 PRD 文档\r\n3. 🤖 交给编程 AI Agent 去实现\r\n4. 🔍 我来测试，提 Bug ，提需求\r\n5. � 循环往复，直到满意\r\n\r\n**就这样，2 天时间，口袋 BBS 诞生了！**\r\n\r\n### 总共代码行 \r\n| Language           | files | blank | comment | code  |\r\n|--------------------|-------|-------|---------|-------|\r\n| Go                 | 84    | 1944  | 1491    | 10494 |\r\n| Vuejs Component    | 39    | 1131  | 2137    | 8594  |\r\n| JavaScript         | 23    | 138   | 248     | 3347  |\r\n| CSS                | 2     | 25    | 19      | 123   |\r\n| SUM:               | 148   | 3238  | 3895    | 22558 |\r\n\r\n## *它只有一个独立的二进制程序，linux 叫 bbsgo ，window 叫 bbsgo.exe ;集成管理后台，主站，本地数据库于一体； 可以放在 U 盘，随时运行；\r\n不得不感叹 AI 的遍历，AI 为了避免初次打开网页光秃秃的没有内容，还贴心的帮我初始化一批图文并茂的数据，太贴心。*\r\n\r\n*代码开源： https://github.com/mageg-x/bbsgo*\r\n\r\n*在线演示： https://bbs.mageg.cn/*", "content_rendered": "<h2>🚀 只用了 2 天，一行代码没写</h2>\n<p>说出来你可能不信，这个项目我一行代码都没写。</p>\n<p>我的工作流程是这样的：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>📝 和 AI 聊需求，确定要做什么功能</li>\n<li>📄 写成详细的 PRD 文档</li>\n<li>🤖 交给编程 AI Agent 去实现</li>\n<li>🔍 我来测试，提 Bug ，提需求</li>\n<li>� 循环往复，直到满意</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>就这样，2 天时间，口袋 BBS 诞生了！</strong></p>\n<h3>总共代码行</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Language</th>\n<th>files</th>\n<th>blank</th>\n<th>comment</th>\n<th>code</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Go</td>\n<td>84</td>\n<td>1944</td>\n<td>1491</td>\n<td>10494</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Vuejs Component</td>\n<td>39</td>\n<td>1131</td>\n<td>2137</td>\n<td>8594</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>JavaScript</td>\n<td>23</td>\n<td>138</td>\n<td>248</td>\n<td>3347</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CSS</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>25</td>\n<td>19</td>\n<td>123</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SUM:</td>\n<td>148</td>\n<td>3238</td>\n<td>3895</td>\n<td>22558</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table><h2>*它只有一个独立的二进制程序，linux 叫 bbsgo ，window 叫 bbsgo.exe ;集成管理后台，主站，本地数据库于一体； 可以放在 U 盘，随时运行；</h2>\n<p>不得不感叹 AI 的遍历，AI 为了避免初次打开网页光秃秃的没有内容，还贴心的帮我初始化一批图文并茂的数据，太贴心。*</p>\n<p><em>代码开源： <a href=\"https://github.com/mageg-x/bbsgo\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/mageg-x/bbsgo</a></em></p>\n<p><em>在线演示： <a href=\"https://bbs.mageg.cn/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://bbs.mageg.cn/</a></em></p>\n", "last_modified": 1775356644, "replies": 29, "id": 1203613}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9226/2bf9/941_large.png?m=1475387237", "name": "rime", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9226/2bf9/941_normal.png?m=1475387237", "title": "中州韻", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/rime", "topics": 147, "footer": "", "header": "聪明的输入法懂我心意", "title_alternative": "RIME", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9226/2bf9/941_mini.png?m=1475387237", "stars": 145, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 941, "parent_node_name": "ime"}, "member": {"id": 717268, "username": "DearFox", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/DearFox", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8df6c11f09cfe84cba114f98f24da53?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8df6c11f09cfe84cba114f98f24da53?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8df6c11f09cfe84cba114f98f24da53?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1730037069, "last_modified": 1774343424, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "shengdr", "last_touched": 1775355251, "title": "是不是折腾输入法的尽头都是回归原生输入法?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203545", "created": 1775299058, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年折腾 rime 输入法,给电脑,手机,家人的,都弄 rime,刚开始还兴致勃勃,有时间就同步一下词库啥的,现在半年没动过,看见用的输入法方案更新,都懒的下载,总是感觉麻烦.还不如用自带的啥都不管", "content_rendered": "<p>去年折腾 rime 输入法,给电脑,手机,家人的,都弄 rime,刚开始还兴致勃勃,有时间就同步一下词库啥的,现在半年没动过,看见用的输入法方案更新,都懒的下载,总是感觉麻烦.还不如用自带的啥都不管</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775299058, "replies": 25, "id": 1203545}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 385, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 391, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 383743, "username": "YanSeven", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/YanSeven", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "我不道啊", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_mini.png?m=1775355387", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_normal.png?m=1775355387", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_large.png?m=1775355387", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_xlarge.png?m=1775355387", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_xxlarge.png?m=1775355387", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f22/feff/383743_xxxlarge.png?m=1775355387", "created": 1550114765, "last_modified": 1775355387, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "evamayy", "last_touched": 1775362165, "title": "怎么感觉 ClaudeCodeMax 5X 额度变少了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203550", "created": 1775303276, "deleted": 0, "content": "是砍额度了，还是说之前在搞什么双倍活动，现在过期了。", "content_rendered": "是砍额度了，还是说之前在搞什么双倍活动，现在过期了。", "last_modified": 1775303276, "replies": 20, "id": 1203550}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 237996, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4476, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 311431, "username": "sjmcefc2", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sjmcefc2", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ed45fe578f1092dcabc2eaaf904f7374?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ed45fe578f1092dcabc2eaaf904f7374?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ed45fe578f1092dcabc2eaaf904f7374?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1524613863, "last_modified": 1524613863, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "sickoo", "last_touched": 1775331239, "title": "哪里有 giffgaff 手机卡", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203525", "created": 1775288660, "deleted": 0, "content": "好像找不到了。", "content_rendered": "<p>好像找不到了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775288660, "replies": 19, "id": 1203525}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_large.png?m=1633251402", "name": "watch", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_normal.png?m=1633251402", "title": " WATCH", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/watch", "topics": 1470, "footer": "", "header": "<a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的智能手表产品", "title_alternative": " WATCH", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_mini.png?m=1633251402", "stars": 589, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 819, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 388030, "username": "iovekkk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/iovekkk", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "永远年轻，永远说话难听", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1490/878c/388030_mini.png?m=1647396803", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1490/878c/388030_normal.png?m=1647396803", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1490/878c/388030_large.png?m=1647396803", "created": 1551332968, "last_modified": 1647396803, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "234ygg", "last_touched": 1775326007, "title": "折腾一下午开通 watch 的高血压检测还是失败了，很无语", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203536", "created": 1775294502, "deleted": 0, "content": "众所周知的方案是使用 anygo 这款软件模拟定位到国外，然后开通，看到网上很多人都用这个方案成功了\r\n不过由于不想付费购买 anygo 会员也不想在自己电脑上运行那个破解的注册机，\r\n然后我心里一想现在 AI 这么火，那么能否用 AI 解决呢？\r\n问了一下 chatGPT ，它回答 anygo 的方案大概也是通过开发者调试机制来模拟定位，这个功能在 xcode 上就有\r\n于是下载了 xcode ，研究了一番（毕竟没做过 iOS 开发），通过 Debug → Simulate Location 模拟了美国纽约的定位。\r\n最终的结果是，天气 app 显示当前位置在纽约，地图 app 显示当前位置在纽约（左下角仍是高德地图），系统时区那里显示时区是纽约\r\n然而健康 app 里面的核对清单里死活就是无法启用，始终显示这个功能在你所在地区不可用。\r\n哎，折腾一下午还是没搞定，真是无语\r\n手机是 iPhone Air ，手表是 s11 ，iPhone 全程魔法，手表全程关机。", "content_rendered": "众所周知的方案是使用 anygo 这款软件模拟定位到国外，然后开通，看到网上很多人都用这个方案成功了<br />不过由于不想付费购买 anygo 会员也不想在自己电脑上运行那个破解的注册机，<br />然后我心里一想现在 AI 这么火，那么能否用 AI 解决呢？<br />问了一下 chatGPT ，它回答 anygo 的方案大概也是通过开发者调试机制来模拟定位，这个功能在 xcode 上就有<br />于是下载了 xcode ，研究了一番（毕竟没做过 iOS 开发），通过 Debug → Simulate Location 模拟了美国纽约的定位。<br />最终的结果是，天气 app 显示当前位置在纽约，地图 app 显示当前位置在纽约（左下角仍是高德地图），系统时区那里显示时区是纽约<br />然而健康 app 里面的核对清单里死活就是无法启用，始终显示这个功能在你所在地区不可用。<br />哎，折腾一下午还是没搞定，真是无语<br />手机是 iPhone Air ，手表是 s11 ，iPhone 全程魔法，手表全程关机。", "last_modified": 1775294502, "replies": 14, "id": 1203536}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 18546, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161", "stars": 8187, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 504190, "username": "shenjialun", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shenjialun", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dea7/686d/504190_mini.png?m=1772209250", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dea7/686d/504190_normal.png?m=1772209250", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dea7/686d/504190_large.png?m=1772209250", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dea7/686d/504190_xlarge.png?m=1772209250", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dea7/686d/504190_xxlarge.png?m=1772209250", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dea7/686d/504190_xxxlarge.png?m=1772209250", "created": 1597651889, "last_modified": 1772209250, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "dizhang", "last_touched": 1775339809, "title": "上海联通 9929 必须接内网？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203547", "created": 1775300683, "deleted": 0, "content": "国际游戏直通车客服说能办，但是宽带要接内网，有办过的朋友知道？", "content_rendered": "国际游戏直通车客服说能办，但是宽带要接内网，有办过的朋友知道？", "last_modified": 1775300683, "replies": 14, "id": 1203547}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/35cf/8659/796_large.png?m=1738938805", "name": "thinkpad", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/35cf/8659/796_normal.png?m=1738938805", "title": "ThinkPad", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/thinkpad", "topics": 98, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "ThinkPad", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/35cf/8659/796_mini.png?m=1738938805", "stars": 92, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 796, "parent_node_name": "Geek"}, "member": {"id": 265982, "username": "infreboot", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/infreboot", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/94e7/be6f/265982_mini.png?m=1772948679", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/94e7/be6f/265982_normal.png?m=1772948679", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/94e7/be6f/265982_large.png?m=1772948679", "created": 1510206056, "last_modified": 1772948679, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "infreboot", "last_touched": 1775320327, "title": "谨慎购入 Thinkbook 14+笔记本，过保后主板故障", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203549", "created": 1775301260, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 笔记本配置\r\n- CPU: 7840H \r\n- 内存: 32G\r\n- 版本：thinkbook 14+ 2023 锐龙版\r\n## 具体表现\r\n- 正常工作中，会突然黑屏，电源灯亮，键盘无反应\r\n- 重启后，键盘灯亮一下，依然黑屏，电源灯亮，键盘无反应\r\n- 静置半小时以上或拔掉电池，能进系统。用一会依然重复上面故障。\r\n- 尝试重装系统，重装系统失败，继续黑屏，电源灯亮，键盘无反应。\r\n\r\n## 售后\r\n- 听到我的描述，售后说估计主板有故障，建议返修，价格 800+\r\n\r\n## 求推荐\r\n- 预算 5k-6k Archlinux 友好型笔记本，不要联想。", "content_rendered": "<h2>笔记本配置</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>CPU: 7840H </li>\n<li>内存: 32G</li>\n<li>版本：thinkbook 14+ 2023 锐龙版</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>具体表现</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>正常工作中，会突然黑屏，电源灯亮，键盘无反应</li>\n<li>重启后，键盘灯亮一下，依然黑屏，电源灯亮，键盘无反应</li>\n<li>静置半小时以上或拔掉电池，能进系统。用一会依然重复上面故障。</li>\n<li>尝试重装系统，重装系统失败，继续黑屏，电源灯亮，键盘无反应。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>售后</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>听到我的描述，售后说估计主板有故障，建议返修，价格 800+</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>求推荐</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>预算 5k-6k Archlinux 友好型笔记本，不要联想。</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1775301329, "replies": 12, "id": 1203549}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_large.png?m=1775237570", "name": "claudecode", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_normal.png?m=1775237570", "title": "Claude Code", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claudecode", "topics": 171, "footer": "善语结善缘，恶语伤人心，勿发广告，会被删帖。", "header": "🤖 欢迎分享&讨论 [Claude Code]( https://claude.com) & Vibe Coding & AI 编程 等相关的话题。  \r\n🈲 发广告或引流内容会被删除", "title_alternative": "Claude Code", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_mini.png?m=1775237570", "stars": 253, "founder_id": 6746, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1202, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 406233, "username": "evamayy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/evamayy", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8af853bd9f5aeb9d7dae7b2eaf89ff47?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8af853bd9f5aeb9d7dae7b2eaf89ff47?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8af853bd9f5aeb9d7dae7b2eaf89ff47?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1556201213, "last_modified": 1773289111, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "evamayy", "last_touched": 1775328466, "title": "Claude 限制在小龙虾上使用了，有什么比较稳定的途径可以解决？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203556", "created": 1775307156, "deleted": 0, "content": "Claude 大面积封号很大的原因就是大家用龙虾疯狂的在调，垃圾 token 太多了，频率太快了，算力太紧张，然后就疯狂的干掉龙虾了\r\n\r\n小龙虾官方给了一个 cli 的过渡方案，但是看下来\r\n- 这是一个临时过渡方案，体验会差一些\r\n- 不支持工具调用\r\n- 没有流式输出\r\n- 会话恢复可能有小问题\r\n- 仍可能需要额外按量付费超出订阅部分", "content_rendered": "<p>Claude 大面积封号很大的原因就是大家用龙虾疯狂的在调，垃圾 token 太多了，频率太快了，算力太紧张，然后就疯狂的干掉龙虾了</p>\n<p>小龙虾官方给了一个 cli 的过渡方案，但是看下来</p>\n<ul>\n<li>这是一个临时过渡方案，体验会差一些</li>\n<li>不支持工具调用</li>\n<li>没有流式输出</li>\n<li>会话恢复可能有小问题</li>\n<li>仍可能需要额外按量付费超出订阅部分</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1775307156, "replies": 12, "id": 1203556}]